                    <msContents>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                            <locus from="3ra" to="57ra"/>
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3942ArdeetCh">Maṣḥafa ʾardǝʾt</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <t:gap xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="ellipsis"/> ዘአሠርቱ፡ ወ፪ቱ፡ አር<t:corr xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ድ</t:corr>እት፡ 
                                ዘከመ፡ ነገሮሙ፡ እግዚእ<t:corr xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ነ</t:corr>፡ ኢየሱስ፡ በዘት<t:corr xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ድ</t:corr>ኅኑ፡ 
                                እም፡ ኃጢአት፡ ወለክሙሂ፡ ንነግረክሙ፡ ንሕነ፡ በዘትድኅኑ፡ እምኵሉ፡ ኃጢአት፡ ነገረ፡ መቅሠፍተ፡ <cb n="3rb"/>እጓለ፡ እመሕያው፡ በዘትድኅኑ፡ እም፡ ኵሉ፡ 
                                ፀራዊ፡ ሕምዘ፡ አርዌ፡ ምድር፡ ወእምኵሉ፡ ሕምዝ፡ ዘይቀትል፡ ነፍስ። ወእምኵሉ፡ ሕማም፡ ወድካመ፡ ሥጋ፡ ወቅጥቃጤ፡ አዕጽምት። በዘትድኅኑ፡ እምኵሉ፡ 
                                <pb n="3va"/> ሰብእ፡ መሰርያን፡ ወዓማፅያን፡ ወበዘትድኅኑ፡ እምስድ<t:corr xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ብ</t:corr>፡ ወእመርገም፡ ወእምኵሎሙ፡ 
                                ዓቃብያነ፡ ሥራይ፡ </incipit>
                            <t:note xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">The text is divided for the days of the week.</t:note>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                            <locus from="59ra" to="81rb"/>
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4002Salotz">Ṣalot za-Muse</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <t:gap xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="ellipsis"/> ጸሎት፡ <t:corr xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ዘ</t:corr>ሙሴ። ንነግረክሙ፡ ንሕነ፡
                                በዘድኅነ፡ ሙሴ፡ እምእዴሁ፡ ለፈርዖን። ጸሎቱ፡ ወስዕለቱ፡ ለሙሴ። ዘወሀቦ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ መግረሬ፡ ፀር፡ ወቀዲሙሰ፡ ወረደ፡ ገብርኤል፡ መልአክ። ወይቤሎ፡ ኢትፍሩህ፡ 
                                ሙሴ፡ ተሰምዓ፡ ጸሎትከ፡ ወስዕ<cb n="59rb"/>ለትከ፡ ኀበ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ </incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                            <locus from="81va" to="83vb"/>
                            <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3646Miracle">Miracle of Mary: Miracle of Mark, son of the king of Rome,
          Gabra ʾIyasus</title>
                            <t:note xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Judging by the incipit, it is probably an abridged version.</t:note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">ተአምሪሃ፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ፡ ጸሎታ፡ ወበረከታ፡ የሃሉ፡ ምስለ፡ ገብራ፡ <t:gap xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="lost"/> 
                                ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን። ወሀሎ፡ ፩ብእሲ፡ ዘስሙ፡ ማርቆስ፡ ዘነግሠ፡ በሮምያ፡ እምድኅረ፡ ሞተ፡ አቡሁ፡ ንጉሥ፡ ዘስሙ፡ ገብረ፡ ኢየሱስ። 
                                ወ<t:corr xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">በ</t:corr>መዋ<t:corr xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ዕ</t:corr>ሊሁ፡ ርትአ፡ <cb n="81vb"/>
                                ሃይማኖተ፡ ክርስቲያን። </incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                            <locus from="83vb" to="85vb"/>
                            <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3977Taammer">Tenth miracle of Gabra Manfas Qǝddus</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">ተአምሪሁ፡ ለአቡነ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4306GabraMa">ገብረ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡</persName> ጸሎቱ፡ ወበረከቱ፡ 
                                የሀሉ፡ <t:corr xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ምስለ፡</t:corr> ገብሩ፡ <t:gap xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="lost"/> ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን። ወነበረ፡ ፩ብእሲ፡ በአሐቲ፡ ኃገር። 
                                ወሰምዓ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ገድሉ፡ ለአቡነ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4306GabraMa">ገብ<pb n="84ra"/>ረ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡</persName> 
                                አመ፭ለመጋቢት፡ ወጠየቀ፡ ውእቱ፡ ለእመ፡ ኮነ፡ ተዝካሩ፡ በጾም፡ </incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                            <locus from="85vb" to="89rb"/>
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5066MiraclesMichael">Miracles of Michael</title>
                            <t:note xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">A miracle of the Archangel Michael: How a poor man borrowed money, became rich, and miraculously sent it back 
                                to the church keeper.</t:note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">ተአምሪሁ፡ ለሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ሚካኤል፡ ትንብልናሁ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስለ፡ <t:corr xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ገብሩ፡</t:corr> 
                                ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አ<pb n="86ra"/>ሜን። ተብህለ፡ ከመ፡ ሀሎ፡ ፩ነዳይ፡ በአሐቲ፡ ኃገር፡ ወጎረ፡ ቤቱ፡ <t:corr xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ቤተ፡</t:corr> 
                                ክርስቲያን። በስመ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ <t:corr xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ወለለ፡</t:corr> ዕለቱ፡ ይገይስ። ውስተ፡ ይእቲ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ 
                                ወይቀውም፡ ቅድመ፡ ሥዕሉ። ለሚካኤል፡ ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ወይስዕል፡ በዓንብዕ፡ ወይብል፡ </incipit>
                        </msItem>
                    </msContents>
